id: main
title: Builtin-only regression flow
description: |
  Single emit.response builtin node. Used by the regression test to assert
  that greentic-pack build no longer requires resolve.json / resolve.summary.json
  entries for builtin nodes (fix/builtin-node-resolve-skip in greentic-pack).
type: messaging
start: emit_response_only
parameters: {}
tags: []
schema_version: 2
entrypoints: {}
nodes:
  emit_response_only:
    routing: out
    emit.response:
      messages:
        - text: "ok"
